      Constructor
      参数:
      row_id - for table display row_index
      student_id - student id shown in the system
      student_name - student name shown in the system
      student_name - email address of the student
      k1_energy - the value of k1
      k2_energy - the value of k2
      k3_trick1 - indicate whether the student have k3 trick 1
      k3_trick2 - indicate whether the student have k3 trick 2
      my_preference - indicate student's preferences to be a team leader
      concerns - student's concerns
